hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2799ccb88383a2b1ce470e22f915fef5be080ddb","tid":328301,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"中共亂改基本法、操縱立法會、旺角義士入獄、本土派沉寂<br />\n<br />\n全部都不及三萬蚊，一聽到人地有學費資助就發癲<br />\n仲要拎唔到現金架，交學費炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係三萬蚊過夜連登仔係雞係鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1287d0595b385a26d3e5d72be1aa8562f4008c84","tid":328301,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得連登好多post都跟隨住舊登部分post嘅風氣<br />\n就係極多重複性高而且冇乜建設性嘅對罵post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來分析個問題根源嘅係少數"},{"pid":"632b50b997feb5cde26224eb570bb3fbcaacab3f","tid":328301,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:17:44.000Z","msg":"睇下果兩個批鬥學生post <br />\n<br />\n幾百個正評、加埋46頁留言<br />\n<br />\n真係癲撚線，人地學生讀書得罪你咩<br />\n講到人地咁廢，讀完都冇前途架啦，咁你班友又晒心機去批鬥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15660bed7f36d4708e0eedc2f41acb2136f43a63","tid":328301,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得連登好多post都跟隨住舊登部分post嘅風氣<br />\n就係極多重複性高而且冇乜建設性嘅對罵post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來分析個問題根源嘅係少數</blockquote><br />\n跟風唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n跟風都跟個正氣小小既好冇<br />\nDQ 4販民果一日，成板都總辭討論同上街post，呢o的值得欣賞<br />\n<br />\n唯一呢個時候 我真係好想販民同左膠上返黎主導下討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b670a2ec54c8a55151236aadd7066aeaf5b415e","tid":328301,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"果36億唔派咪又係射落海<br />\n幾時輪到落你袋<img src=\"/assets/fac